Adding the container was followed from this guide: 

https://docs.pi-hole.net/docker/

There were some slight hiccups
1. There was no stated password
### to circumvent this, delete the API password that it has

run :
sudo docker exec -it pihole pihole setpassword

This will prompt you to create a password

To access pi hole:
http://(IP of PI)/admin

if you do not include the /admin it will give a redirect link anyway.
